## 2.7 Price Manipulation Paradoxes

### Purpose

State constraints that price impact models must satisfy to avoid artificial profit opportunities from round-trip trades.

The section connects:

- Price manipulation.
- Impact decay.
- Liquidity changes.
- Volume predictions.

