## Key formulas to preserve

- Price impact:
  $$I=P-S.$$

- Trade price:
  $$\tilde P_{t-}=S_{t-}+I_{t-}+s_{t-}.$$

- Cash update:
  $$\Delta_nK^N=-\tilde P_{n-1}^N\Delta_nQ^N.$$

- Accounting P&L:
  $$X_n^N=P_n^NQ_n^N+K_n^N.$$

- Fundamental P&L:
  $$Y_n^N=S_n^NQ_n^N+K_n^N.$$

- Discrete accounting self-financing equation:
  $$\Delta_n X^N
  =
  Q_{n-1}^N\Delta_n P^N
  -
  s_{n-1}^N\Delta_n Q^N
  +
  \Delta_n P^N\Delta_n Q^N.$$

- Discrete fundamental self-financing equation:
  $$\Delta_n Y^N
  =
  Q_{n-1}^N\Delta_n S^N
  -
  I_{n-1}^N\Delta_n Q^N
  -
  s_{n-1}^N\Delta_n Q^N
  +
  \Delta_n S^N\Delta_n Q^N.$$

- OW microstructure impact:
  $$\Delta_nI^N=-\beta I_{n-1}^N\Delta t^N+\lambda\Delta_nQ^N.$$

- OW reduced-form impact:
  $$dI_t=-\beta I_tdt+\lambda dQ_t.$$

- OW fundamental P&L:
  $$dY_t=Q_tdS_t-I_tdQ_t-\frac{1}{2}d[I,Q]_t.$$

- Alpha signal:
  $$\alpha_t=\mathbb E[S_T-S_t\mid\mathcal F_t].$$

- Alpha identity:
  $$\mathbb E\left[\int_0^T Q_tdS_t\right]
  =
  \mathbb E\left[\int_0^T\alpha_tdQ_t+[\alpha,Q]_T\right].$$

- Impact-space inverse map:
  $$dQ_t=\frac{1}{\lambda}(\beta I_tdt+dI_t).$$

- Liquidation constraint in impact space:
  $$I_T+\int_0^T\beta I_tdt=-\lambda Q_0.$$

- OW martingale-price optimal impact:
  $$I_t^*=-\frac{\lambda}{2+\beta T}Q_0,
  \quad t\in(0,T).$$

- OW martingale-price optimal trading:
  $$dQ_t^*=-\frac{\beta}{2+\beta T}Q_0dt.$$

- Deterministic-alpha optimal impact:
  $$I_t^*
  =
  \frac{1}{2}
  \left(
  \alpha_t-\beta^{-1}\alpha_t'+\nu
  \right).$$

- Deterministic-alpha multiplier:
  $$\nu
  =
  -\frac{1}{2+\beta T}
  \left(
  2\lambda Q_0
  +
  \alpha_0
  +
  \beta\int_0^T\alpha_tdt
  \right).$$

- Stochastic-alpha unconstrained optimal impact:
  $$I_t^*
  =
  \frac{1}{2}
  \left(
  \alpha_t+\beta^{-1}\mu_t
  \right).$$

- Time-changed OW:
  $$dI_t=-\beta\tau_t'I_tdt+\lambda dQ_t.$$

- Generalized OW:
  $$dI_t=-\beta_tI_tdt+\lambda_tdQ_t.$$

- Stochastic liquidity:
  $$\lambda_t=e^{\gamma_t}.$$

- No-manipulation condition:
  $$2\beta_t+\gamma_t'>0.$$

- External total impact:
  $$d\bar I_t=-\beta_t\bar I_tdt+\lambda_t(dQ_t+dM_t).$$

- Own impact:
  $$dI_t=-\beta_tI_tdt+\lambda_tdQ_t.$$

- Square-root volume-liquidity scaling:
  $$\lambda_t\propto v_t^{-1/2}.$$

- Volume-growth no-manipulation bound:
  $$\frac{v_t'}{v_t}<4\beta_t.$$

